data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to own a home in this fantastic location! Close to EVERYTHING - Downtown,Shopping,Schools - Easy access to the I565. All one level and Full Brick! The yard is level with Pecan Trees that produce delicious bounty, the covered front porch is great for sitting & visiting and the back deck is large enough for a friendly cook out. ***New Roof and Heating and Cooling in 2023.*** Inside offers a great floorplan-Bright Living/Dining Room, Eat-in Kitchen w/Great Counter & Cabinet Space, the den/study offers plenty of space for game day gatherings and leads to the deck.
